elets. Finally, we present the\nresults of a novel simulation of multiple solid deformable objects in a\nviscoelastic medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Jul 2018 01:11:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Nov 2018 19:17:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Mar 2019 17:53:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-11"}
