ions, the experiment performed here\ndemonstrates the success of the current numerical models in EAGLE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Jul 2018 07:16:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Sep 2018 09:51:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-19"}
